Package: FAVA
Title: An FST-Based Assessment of Variability across Vectors of Relative Abundances
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Maike", "Morrison", , "maikem@stanford.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0430-1401"))
Description: Implements the statistic FAVA, an FST-based Assessment of Variability across vectors of relative Abundances, as well as a suite of helper functions which enable the visualization and statistical analysis of relative abundance data. The FAVA R package accompanies the paper, “Quantifying compositional variability in microbial communities with FAVA” by Morrison et al. (2024).
